Lumpy skin disease, Russia
--------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 01 Aug 2017 from Dr Evgeny Nepoklonov, vice-minister, Ministry of Agriculture, Ministry of Agriculture, Moscow, Russia

Summary
Report type: follow-up report no. 5
Date of start of the event: 05 Jun 2017
Date of confirmation of the event: 09 Jun 2017
Reason for notification: recurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 15 Feb 2017
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: lumpy skin disease virus
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, Laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks (4)
Outbreak 1: Nalivnaya, Sovetsky, Saratovskaya oblast
Date of start of the outbreak: 17 Jul 2017
