Control measures
Measures applied: movement control inside the country, vaccination in response to the outbreak(s), screening, quarantine, official disposal of carcasses, by-products and waste, zoning, disinfection, disinfestation, process to inactivate the pathogenic agent in products or by-products, treatment of affected animals
